---
import SectionWrapper from '../SectionWrapper.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<div class="guide-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<SectionWrapper bg="base" id="guide" class="guide-section">
  <!-- Section label -->
  <p class="section-label">// 04 THE GUIDE</p>

  <!-- Headline -->
  <h2 class="guide-headline">
    <span>You approve the strategy.</span>
    <span>Then we write the code.</span>
  </h2>

  <!-- Two-column layout -->
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <!-- LEFT column: guide copy -->
    <div class="guide-copy">
      <div class="guide-body">
        <p>
          Every failed project we've ever seen had the same root cause: the answer
          was sold before the question was asked. The designer built the design.
          The developer wrote the code. Nobody stopped to ask whether the message
          made sense to a stranger.
        </p>

        <p>
          We start differently. Before any code is written, we produce a Problem
          Statement. It's a plain-language document that defines exactly what's
          broken and what the fix looks like. You read it. You verify it. You sign
          off on it. Then we build.
        </p>

        <p>
          One person handles your project from discovery to launch. No handoffs.
          No "the other person had that file." No explaining your business twice.
          When it ships, it comes with a Handoff Package: your code, your
          credentials, your documentation. Everything you need to run it without us.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you never call us again after launch, that's a win. That's what the
          Handoff Package is for.
        </p>

        <p class="guide-closing">
          That's Maximum Execution, based in Richmond, Virginia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT column: testimonials -->
    <div class="proof-col">
      <div class="testimonials">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-body">
            "They understood the problem before they started building. That had
            never happened with any agency we'd worked with before."
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-header">
            <cite class="log-meta">Client testimonial coming soon</cite>
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-body">
            "I actually understand what I own now. The handoff documentation was
            better than anything I've received from a team twice the size."
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-header">
            <cite class="log-meta">Client testimonial coming soon</cite>
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p class="testimonial-body">
            "The diagnostic found two problems I didn't know I had. We fixed both
            in the same build. Our lead flow doubled in the first month."
          </p>
          <p class="testimonial-header">
            <cite class="log-meta">Client testimonial coming soon</cite>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="guide-cta">
    <Button variant="primary" href="#diagnostic">[START YOUR PROJECT &gt;]</Button>
  </div>
</SectionWrapper>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .guide-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* Section label */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Headline - Geist Sans, two lines */
  .guide-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-4);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-snug);
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .guide-headline span {
    display: block;
  }

  .guide-headline span:first-child {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .guide-headline span:last-child {
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.7);
  }

  /* Two-column grid */
  .guide-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 4fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  /* ── Guide copy column ── */
  .guide-body {
    max-width: var(--measure-normal);
  }

  .guide-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .guide-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .guide-closing {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text) !important;
  }

  /* ── Proof column ── */
  .proof-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  /* ── Testimonials — frosted glass ── */
  .testimonials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .testimonial {
    background: oklch(0.20 0.09 62 / 0.8);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-5) var(--space-6);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .testimonial-body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--step-0);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .testimonial-header {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .log-meta {
    color: var(--amber-2);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .guide-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* ── Desktop sticky scroll for copy ── */
  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .guide-copy {
      position: sticky;
      top: 80px;
      align-self: start;
    }
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .guide-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-3);
    }

    .guide-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .guide-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
